name: Catbal
description: Catbal is a memecoin created via Hypurr Fun Bot, Hyperliquid equivalent of Solana's pump.fun. It centers around two intertwined topics: cats and cabals or secret organizations. The content is playful, refers various art works, historical bits and community sourced memes. Catbal's intention is to evolve into a full fledge Intellectual Property, covering images, animations, comic book strips, mobile apps and games, NFTs and more.
